              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/24739876/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/45586308/" class=" " title="阿湫儿">阿湫儿</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="24739876">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">看此书，是为了纪念一段过往。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-02-22 11:20</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                看此书，是为了纪念一段过往。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
